---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 399
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=Killing the Inward Dragon
By: St Thomas Aquinas
---
S. Martin ascended from the military state to the clerical, for the
army of the Church is higher in status than the army of the world; its
warfare is a higher one, and its soldiers fight against spiritual
enemies.
